{"word":"μαίομαι","slug":"μαίομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μαίομαι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>*<el>μάω</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to seek</i>:<p/></div><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to endeavour, strive</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <i>to search, examine</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to seek after, seek for</i>, <el>τι</el> <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>: <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> <i>to seek</i> to do, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}